name: great! angle! babe!
description: our marriage is failing. but perhaps. this picture will accumulate. enough likes to save us. to dissolve our resentment. to shove our two idiotic faces into the feeds of uninterested friends and family. who can sense the suffering behind out insufferable grins. maybe i'll bleed out in this retention pond. maybe you'll use my arm in future travels. maybe we'll be together forever.
